<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f6f9fc; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #1a56db; color: white !important; font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 8px; }
    .text-link { color: #1a56db; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: underline; }
    .credentials-box { background-color: #f3f4f6; border-left: 4px solid #1a56db; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .credential-row { margin: 8px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .warning { color: #d97706; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 15px; }
    .cta-wrap { text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dlfzzfdx0/image/upload/v1777286182/Brand_title_with_tagline-removebg-preview_jpjpet.png" alt="Proteccio Data" style="width: 200px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;">
      <p style="color:#2ecc71; margin:0; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:1px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">
          Data Privacy • Compliance • Implementation
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <h2 style="color: #111827; margin-top: 0;">Welcome to Proteccio CMS</h2>
    
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your account has been successfully created on the <strong>Consent Management System</strong> by your administrator.</p>
    
    <p>Here are your temporary credentials to log in:</p>
    
    <div class="credentials-box">
      <div class="credential-row"><strong>Username / Email:</strong> Please use the same email address where you received this welcome message.</div>
      <div class="credential-row"><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <code style="background: #e5e7eb; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; font-family: monospace;">{{tempPassword}}</code></div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="warning">⚠️ Important: You will be required to change this password immediately upon your first login for security reasons.</p>
    
    <div class="cta-wrap">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 15px;">
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="text-link">Open Proteccio CMS</a>
      </p>
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn">Log In &amp; Reset Password</a>
    </div>
    
    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions or need assistance, please reach out to your system administrator.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Proteccio Data Privacy. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
